note over browser:
user types comment
to the text field
end note

note over browser:
user clicks
submit button
end note

note over browser:
new note appended to
the list of notes,
page rerendered
end note

browser -> server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa

note over server:
server add new note
to list of notes 
end note

server -> browser: Status Code 201